# 3D vector dot product (positional fields).
*mk3(x as i64, y as i64, z as i64) returns Vec of i64
    v is vec()
    v.push(x)
    v.push(y)
    v.push(z)
    v

*dot3(a as Vec of i64, b as Vec of i64) returns i64
    a.get(0) * b.get(0) + a.get(1) * b.get(1) + a.get(2) * b.get(2)

*main
    a is mk3(1, 2, 3)
    b is mk3(4, 5, 6)
    log dot3(a, b)
